data.description: PRICE REDUCED - Seller will cover full 2024 HOA dues and will consider helping with rate buy-down. Beautiful newer construction home in the gated community of Villas at Desert Horizon. Ready to move in, this home is turnkey! Immaculate from top to bottom with a whole new backyard makeover, new alum-wood back patio cover, new side gates and more! Enjoy this split floor plan with an open kitchen/great-room concept and tasteful finishes throughout the home. This home still feels like a brand-new home! Deep two-car garage and Rv gate makes for great space for any toys & tools. Enjoy the picuresque mountain views from the back patio and the convenient community pool. This home would make a wonderful primary home or even perfect for a winter visitor to come and enjoy!
